name: miniprosjekt-datasett
description: I wish to create a tool that gives a bit of intel in the local bus offer. I want to create a map of all the active busses, as well as show how delayed they are. Maybe also develop a system that shows the average delay time of different lines, as well as an AI that predicts how delayed a bus will be based on traffic and other factors. Though these are far more complex than the basic features I will start off with.
author: saileeich
